{"id":6259,"date":"2023-03-20T13:56:00","date_gmt":"2023-03-20T13:56:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/?p=6259"},"modified":"2023-03-29T07:26:17","modified_gmt":"2023-03-29T07:26:17","slug":"keren-bangg-crystalone-borong-piala-tingkat-nasional","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/2023\/03\/20\/keren-bangg-crystalone-borong-piala-tingkat-nasional\/","title":{"rendered":"Keren &#038; Bangga! Crystalone Borong Piala Tingkat Nasional"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Student Company merupakan perusahaan siswa yang dibentuk pada tahun 2022.<br>Dengan produk unggulan mereka yaitu Tawas Spray Deodorant.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam kejuaraan perusahaan pelajar se indonesia.&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/crystalone.sc\/\">@crystalone.sc<\/a>&nbsp;mengikuti PJI Company of the year competition<br>Yang bertempat di Kota Kasablanka Mall Jakarta<br>Pada Tanggal 18 Maret 2023<br>Yang diselenggarakan oleh Prestasi junior indonesia.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Crystalone borong kategori The best finnancial management l,<br>Young entrepreneur choice award,<br>The best student company in Regional,<br>2nd runner up in Indonesia.<br>Selamat &amp; Sukses&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/crystalone.sc\/\">@crystalone.sc<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/336000366_535700658686085_4617713590919144911_n-800x800.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6260\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/336000366_535700658686085_4617713590919144911_n.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/?attachment_id=6260#main\" class=\"wp-image-6260\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/336000366_535700658686085_4617713590919144911_n-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-cont